{"tid":1045640,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆去廁所好奇怪","createTime":"2019-03-03T17:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T06:40:58.000Z","uid":215575,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1b22c9125b75b1457b3b28909f6c4e49218bd8","tid":1045640,"uid":215575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:17:55.000Z","msg":"搬咗屋一年多發覺每日起身刷牙嘅時候都聞到廁所嘅浴室位有陣怪味本來冇為意但情況過咗一排實在太臭終於係我一次機緣巧合之下發現到原來老竇對住個浴室位屙尿然後求其開個花灑沖一沖以為乾淨但係到我用嘅時候真係好臭仲衰過屙尿唔沖廁又唔知點解佢唔肯用馬桶。所以想問下好唔好叫佢以後都唔好再喺浴室位屙尿<br />\n<br />\n正皮：唔俾面直接叫<br />\n負皮：俾個面唔講話晒都係老竇<br />\n<br />\n示意圖<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/011150_10a9a8c9ee60852f3008f60bf5f44228.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F011150_10a9a8c9ee60852f3008f60bf5f44228.png&h=e2cd408b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d91aa57fb6704cd0b9a59b5cd3d362045be460d1","tid":1045640,"uid":226216,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:24:39.000Z","msg":"其實有標點符號存在"},{"pid":"4bf894ab7a1c15365547bdf43b25c33a8aad1423","tid":1045640,"uid":226216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:25:07.000Z","msg":"你知唔知？"},{"pid":"f420f20b064c927ee2fb6c89755c6d6cba2efa11","tid":1045640,"uid":143391,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:26:46.000Z","msg":"請問影成個廁所既用意喺邊？"},{"pid":"6ce169bdfc7c7449d995e4f176b9218ca2aecf82","tid":1045640,"uid":204537,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T17:27:19.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朝早晨勃落唔切黎，又趕住出門口就唯有疴住落浴缸先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係為勢所逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p